Package: enrichmet
Type: Package
Title: ENRICHMET: R package for Quick and Easy Pathway and Network Analyses in Metabolomics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yonatan Ayalew Mekonnen
Maintainer: Yonatan <yonatanayalew.mekonnen@moffitt.org>
Description: Provides functions to perform metabolite-based pathway enrichment 
    analysis using Fisher’s exact test and MetSEA. Computes relative betweenness 
    centrality (RBC) of input metabolites in a pathway-metabolite interaction network. 
    The package generates visualizations including pathway dot plots, MetSEA plots, 
    and metabolite centrality plots. It supports KEGG-based pathway inputs and 
    generates exportable results.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
